rror) {\n            if (!NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)) {\n                throw error;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static class InlineOrderService {\n        private final String source;\n        private final int basePrice;\n\n        public InlineOrderService(String source, int basePrice) {\n            this.source = source == null ? \"default\" : source;\n            this.basePrice = basePrice;\n        }\n\n        public int price(String sku, int quantity) {\n            return basePrice + sku.length() + quantity;\n        }\n\n        public String describe(String sku) {\n            return source + \" \" + sku;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1781189727223}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_jW4ZGwTbnBGyxUGZOFD3nUvH|fc_0ec753bfee22910d016a2acc5edbac8190ba0e76c30e537040", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/mihailo/git/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/3997-4ea59083/local_repositories/source_context/org.mockito/mockito-core/5.0.0/main/extracted/org/mockito/internal/creation/bytebuddy/InlineDelegateByteBuddyMockMaker.java'"}], "details": {}, "isError": true, "timestamp": 1781189727223}]}
